 (\n...\nHubSpot, Salesloft, ZoomInfo, DealHub CPQ) end-to-end ▪️Built pipeline, forecasting, and lifecycle frameworks from the ground up, improving forecasting accuracy by 25% ▪️Designed executive dashboards for CAC, LTV, ARR, and funnel metrics powering board reporting ▪️Partnered with Sales, Marketing, and Finance on lead routing, lifecycle stages, and comp alignment ▪️Identified funnel bottlenecks and optimized workflows for faster deal velocity and cleaner data ▪️Managed vendor relationships and influenced platform decisions through structured business reviews 💾 Stack:\n...\n, HubSpot, ChurnZero, Salesloft, ZoomInfo, DealHub CPQ, Tableau, Netsuite, Zuora"
